import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    data.boxplot(column='avg_income', by='region', ax=ax)
    ax.set_title('What is the distribution of average income across different regions?')
    ax.set_xlabel('Region')
    ax.set_ylabel('Average Income')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.legend(title='Regions', loc='upper right')
    plt.suptitle('')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    group_counts = data['group'].value_counts()
    plt.pie(group_counts, labels=group_counts.index, autopct='%1.1f%%')
    plt.title('What is the proportion of each group in the dataset?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend(group_counts.index, loc='upper right')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    scatter = ax.scatter(data['total'], data['pct'], c=data['group'].astype('category').cat.codes, cmap='viridis')
    legend1 = ax.legend(*scatter.legend_elements(), title="Groups")
    ax.add_artist(legend1)
    plt.xlabel('Total')
    plt.ylabel('Pct')
    plt.title('What is the relationship between total and pct?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='pct', hue='region', multiple='stack', legend=True)
    plt.title('What is the distribution of pct across different regions?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Pct')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.legend(title='Region', loc='upper right')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    avg_total_by_group = data.groupby('group')['total'].mean()
    ax = avg_total_by_group.plot(kind='bar', color=['blue', 'green', 'red', 'cyan', 'magenta', 'yellow', 'black'])
    plt.title('What is the average total by group?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Group')
    plt.ylabel('Average Total')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.legend(['Average Total'])
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
